The package is provide by LTRC, IIIT Hyderabad.

Dependencies (to be installed before installation): g++,gcc,bash,perl
Get the package.
  - wget http://ltrc.iiit.ac.in/analyzer/hindi/shallow-parser-hin-4.0.fc8.tar.gz
  - Refer shallow-parser-hin-4.0.fc8/INSTALL for installation
  
The package provides the parsing at various levels.
For postags: 
  - After running the parser.
  - postags will be stored in OUTPUT.tmp/postagger.tmp

To get output in good format:
  - Run correctFormatPostags.py OUTPUT.tmp/postagger.tmp

